high_descs: Turn around, move forward slightly, then turn right and head to the oven
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the counter
Turn around and head to the wall, then turn right and move forward to the window, then turn right and move forward to the white door and turn right again to face the black container
look down at the black container and cut a piece of the tomato off

turn right and move forward to the white door, then turn left and move forward towards the refrigerator, the turn left and move forward slightly towards the oven, then turn right and head to the coffee maker
put the knife on the counter to the right of the fork and in front of the coffee maker
turn right and move forward slightly, then turn right and head to the window, then turn right and move forward to the white door, then turn right and face the black container
pick up the sliced tomato piece from the container
turn right and head to the white door, then turn left and move forward to the white refrigerator

open the refrigerator, place the tomato slice in the refrigerator, then close the refrigerator, wait a short time, then open the refrigerator and take out the tomato slice, then close the refrigerator
turn left, then move forward slightly, then turn right to face the coffee maker
put the tomato slice on the counter to the right of the knife and in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of tomato in front of the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn left, go to the counter to the left of stove top.
Take the knife above the bowl on the counter.
Turn around, go to the end of the counter, make a right, go past the counter, make a right, go towards the floor, face the black bin to the right.
Cut the tomato in the bin into pieces.
Go right, go to the end of the counter, turn left, go past the counter, go towards the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the knife in front of the coffee maker on the counter.
Turn around, go straight past the counter to the window, turn right, go to the door, turn right and face the black bin.
Take a slice of tomato from the bin.
Turn right, go straight past the counter, turn left, go straight to the fridge.
Put the tomato on the bottom shelf of the fridge in front of the green cup. Close then open the fridge door. Take the tomato from the fridge.
Go to the left to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Put the tomato to the left of the pepper on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of tomato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the right towards the stove.
Pick up the knife next to a white bowl on the counter top
Turn around, walk straight, turn right, and walk straight towards the black trash can next to the yellow chair.
Cut the tomato inside the black trash can
Bring the knife, turn around, walk straight to the other side of the room, turn left and walk towards the coffee maker on the counter top.
Put the knife next to the fork near the coffee maker.
go to the right, turn right, walk straight before turning right again, walk straight back to the black trash can.
Pick up the slice of tomato from the trash can.
Walk to the right, turn left and walk straight to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the tomato slice in front of the green glass, close the refrigerator, wait for a few seconds, open the refrigerator, pick up the slice of tomato and close the refrigerator.
Walk to the left towards the coffee maker on the counter top.
Put the slice of tomato in front of the coffee maker, next to the knife on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of tomato next the knife on the counter top.
